title: Cisco 79XX Firmware, Sounds and Example Configuration
description:
I pulled my hair out trying to find these files for my Cisco 7940.  The Cisco website really sucks hard and they charge for this crap so I eventually found them on some random FTP mirror with some .nl TLD.

It includes a collection of (SIP) firmware / ringtones and example configuration files for the Cisco 79XX series IP Phones.

Hopefully this will save telephony geeks some time.

(This also includes the ringtone from the TV series "24")
